BBK01.WT5013: Exchange rates on the Frankfurt exchange /SEK 100 = DM ... / Sweden

General: Spot middle rates in Deutsche Mark; difference between buying or selling rate in D-Mark: 0.080 up to the end of 1993 / 0.060 since 1994. From 18 May 1953 to 30 December 1998 official quotation on the Frankfurt exchange. From January 1999, euro reference exchange rates of the European Central Bank; see wt5634. Our specific comments refer to "Frankfurt exchange closed on ..." (Devisenbrse am ... geschlossen) or "Quotation suspended on ..." (Notierung am ... ausgesetzt).
